# Level 1 Workflow: Quick Bug Fix

Level 1 tasks are isolated bug fixes affecting a single component. Prioritize speed — but never skip the test.

## Workflow Phases

```mermaid
graph LR
    Start(("Complexity Analysis")) --> NikoBuild["🐱 build"]
    NikoBuild --> NikoQA{"🐱 qa"}
    NikoQA -->|"PASS"| Done("Done")
    NikoQA -->|"FAIL"| NikoBuild
```

Level 1 tasks skip `/plan`, `/creative`, and `/preflight`. Go straight to build.
Level 1 tasks are *simple* so there's no `/reflect` or `/archive` after building, either. A commit message & description are sufficient record.

## Build Phase

Load `.cursor/rules/shared/niko/level1/level1-build.mdc` and follow the instructions.

## QA Phase

Load `.cursor/commands/shared/niko/qa.md` and follow the instructions.
